      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPEED LEE (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when eighth at Cannington over 520m behind Hum Bug Monelli (30.85) in a Novice race. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can make amends. SMELL LIKE ROSE (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 28.17 beating DODGY SHADOW. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. DODGY DANNY (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.3 lengths away in third (28.26) behind SMELL LIKE ROSE at this track. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Leading chance. DODGY SHADOW (3) has top-three aspirations after placing last time.",
